public interface IDataTypeDefinition extends IDataDescribingComponent
Interface to the data type definition class A datatype contains some data object definition. I.e. a complex datatype might be "student" containing 3 String fields: "name", "sirname" and "university". A data object definitions would be "John", "Doe", "KIT", with the datatype "student". The datatype is defining the structure, the data object is the instance
